title: 이달의소녀탐구 #332 (LOONA TV #332)
summary:
Olivia Hye and JinSoul are filming the Choreography for Egoist
0:05 -- Bluebetta JinSoul is ready! Practicing the dance steps for her
Rap part in front of Mr. Choreographer.
0:12 -- JinSoul running behind the dancers but ending up to be too early to show up.
0:18 -- JinSoul talking about how embarrassing it was for her to miss the timing.
0:24 -- Now she's on the right timing HAHA
0:32 -- JinSoul talking about herself making a few mistakes in the first filming
0:35 -- "However it's gonna be different this time, because I'm a professional!"
0:43 -- The neon sign of "Fallen Angel" written in Chinese is being discussed.
0:48 -- Also the cans we see in the MV which displays JinSoul's english translation
of one of the verses in her song, Singing in the Rain.
